name: 3-Top Rotating Side Table
description: The 3-Top Rotating Side Table is completely mobile, allowing one to adjust the piece to their preference from elongated to clustered. Currently made to order 8-10 weeks. Handmade; Shagreen surface, bronze-patina brass legs; Wipe clean with soft dry cloth; Made in Philippines. Although inspired by her parents, Kifu's collection is a distinct identity of its own, reflecting youth and whimsy.
